t; background-color: transparent !important; display: inline-block;">
<span>[11]</span>
</a> =E2=80=94 so it is not an illegal securities exchange. <a href=3D"http=
s://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/32082673.275409/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuY=
mxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDctMTMvY3J5cHRvY3VycmVuaWVzLWp1=
